body:
It's not good to have default values of [functions to be mutable elements](http://python-guide-pt-br.readthedocs.io/en/latest/writing/gotchas/). Might be better to set it to `None` and create the dict inside the function
```python
def fun(initializer=None):
    if initializer is None:
        initializer = dict()
```

